{"title":"炉前锻工","authors":["李善庆"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":1,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉前锻工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长春汽车公司工人  李善庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻锤冬冬震九霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火花飞舞照天烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉前腾腾烟雾滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人欢马啸掀浪潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀浪潮，干劲高！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱锻工胸怀宽广心如火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上汗水似雨浇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑红的肩膀连铁臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握大锤志不摇："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇困难，猛冲猛闯脚下踩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇关键，猛打猛擂狠狠敲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁钻上，多少钢花烂熳开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞅炉前，烟火飞腾龙虎跃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问干劲哪里来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席语录炉前挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字如灯心上雕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心上雕，如灯照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命立场站得牢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落锤好比春雷响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬锤好比掀风暴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红手巧人人赞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都夸咱的锻件好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，好锻件，锻件好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经百锻，经千烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷轰电击摧不毁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打不弯腰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命汽车装上它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬山越岭笛声高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代的车轮永向前呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山大海不抛锚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《汽车工人》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}